UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2243
1 AN ACT relating to land use.
2 Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 Section 1. KRS 100.283 is amended to read as follows:
4 After the approval of a subdivision plat by the planning commission, it shall be recorded
5 at the expense of the subdivider in the office of the county clerk. The plat shall be in the
6 form of a rectangle and the clerk shall not be required to record a plat exceeding twenty-
7 four (24) inches on one (1) side and thirty-six (36) inches on the other. The county clerk
8 shall provide a plat cabinet with an appropriate index for those plats which are too large
9 to be placed in a plat book.
